Member Enumeration Documentation

enum ExpandStringLane::laneDirection
 

The directions of a lane, a lane can have more than one direction.

Enumeration values:
no_dir  no direction indicated
sharp_left  sharp left (135 degrees)
left  left (90 degrees)
half_left  half left (45 degrees)
ahead  ahead
half_right  half right (45 degrees)
right  right (90 degrees)
sharp_right  sharp right (135 degrees)
uturn_left  U-Turn Left (180 degrees).
uturn_right  U-Turn Right (180 degrees).
opposite_direction  If lane is in the opposite direction.
preferred_lane  preferred lane, not a directon just stored internally.
not_car_lane  not allowed to drive in with car, not a directon just stored internally.
